### Aplica deltas (evento 3D)
POST /api/v1/3d/scores HTTP/1.1
Host: localhost:3000
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <SEU_TOKEN_AQUI>

{
  "deltas": {
    "blue": 3,
    "red": -1,
    "green": 4
  }
  // "occurredAt": "2025-08-14T16:05:00.000Z"  // opcional
}

###

### Soma por faixa horária no dia local corrente (sem 'date')
# Ex.: 14:00–15:00 no fuso America/Sao_Paulo
GET /api/v1/3d/scores?from=14:00&to=15:00&tz=America/Sao_Paulo HTTP/1.1
Host: localhost:3000
Content-Type: application/json

###

### (Opcional) Filtrar por um time específico (id é string)
GET /api/v1/3d/scores?from=19:30&to=21:00&teamId=blue&tz=America/Sao_Paulo HTTP/1.1
Host: localhost:3000
Content-Type: application/json
